title: Antonio Brown Comeback; Vikings Deep Dive with Drew Magary
itunes:title: Antonio Brown Comeback; Vikings Deep Dive with Drew Magary
description:
A bunker filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler and Gregg Rosenthal bring you all of the latest news in the NFL including a few teams discussing on bringing back Antonio Brown (10:29), Martha Firestone Ford stepping down as Detroit Lions owner (14:50) and Big Ben discussing some his past demons (27:03). Drew Magary stops by beachside to do a deep dive on the Minnesota Vikings (32:56).
